 <span class="snippet-span">
  <div class="brailled"><pre>⠼⠉⠲⠀⠭⠐⠓⠉⠋⠭⠭⠨⠙⠉⠀⠣⠚⠉⠊⠭⠨⠛⠉⠑⠉⠡⠚⠉⠀⠹⠥⠣⠅
</pre></div>
